Package org.neo4j.kernel.impl.util.collection

Class LinearProbeLongLongHashMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.collections.impl.primitive.AbstractLongIterable
      • org.neo4j.kernel.impl.util.collection.LinearProbeLongLongHashMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable, org.eclipse.collections.api.LongIterable, org.eclipse.collections.api.map.primitive.LongLongMap, org.eclipse.collections.api.map.primitive.LongValuesMap, org.eclipse.collections.api.map.primitive.MutableLongLongMap, org.eclipse.collections.api.map.primitive.MutableLongValuesMap, org.eclipse.collections.api.PrimitiveIterable, Resource
    class LinearProbeLongLongHashMap
extends org.eclipse.collections.impl.primitive.AbstractLongIterable
implements org.eclipse.collections.api.map.primitive.MutableLongLongMap, Resource
    Off heap implementation of long-long hash map.
    • It is not thread-safe
    • It has to be closed to prevent native memory leakage
    • Iterators returned by this map are fail-fast
